paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
with cte as(
    select * from(
        select TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000)) as date, guid, sessionId, utmContent, utmSource, utmCampaign 
        from `last125Days(appLaunch)` 
        where TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(timestamp/1000))>='2022-12-01'
        union 
        select TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(startTime/1000)) as date, firstGuid as guid, sessionId, utmContent, utmSource, utmCampaign 
        from `last125Days(sessionSummary)` 
        where TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(startTime/1000))>='2022-12-01'
    ) order by guid
)

select date, count (distinct case when lower(utmContent) like '%dpanew%' then sessionId end) as visits
from cte 
group by date 
order by date desc

",1000)

run(sql="
with cte as(
    select distinct b.orderDate, 
                    b.subOrderId, 
                    b.Channel
    from `temp.d` a 
    left join (
                select distinct a.orderDate, 
                                a.subOrderId,
                                a.Channel, 
                                b.pogId
                from `temp.order_sd_2` a 
                left join `all(agCmDump)` b 
                on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId
                where a.orderDate>='2023-02-15'
            )b 
    on a.pog_id=b.pogId
)

select orderDate as date, count(distinct subOrderId) as SD_Orders, count(distinct case when lower(Channel) like '%fb%' then subOrderId end) as FB_orders 
from cte 
group by orderDate
order by orderDate

",1000)

run(sql="
with cte as(
    select distinct b.date, 
                    b.sessionId,
                    b.utmContent
    from `temp.d` a 
    left join (
                select distinct to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((timestamp)/1000)) as date, 
                                pogId,
                                sessionId,
                                utmContent
                from `last56Days(productView)`
            )b 
    on a.pog_id=b.pogId
)

select date, count(distinct sessionId) as SD_Sessions, count(distinct case when lower(utmContent) like '%dpanew%' then sessionId end) as FB_Sessions 
from cte 
group by date
order by date

",1000)
